{"tid":2389562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擬以BNO移英港人情侶到簽證中心交文件　擔心日後遭阻礙","createTime":"2021-02-01T04:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T15:01:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a530933dc7dd8d77c745535f4ca1fc81fdf386e7","tid":2389562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573410-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573410-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f64dcf61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573410-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=657c0b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573410-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國推出的BNO港人居留簽證計劃昨日起接受申請，身處香港的人士可透過英國政府網站填寫申請表，再預約到北角的簽證中心提供指紋和辦理手續。<br />\n<br />\n情侶Jason和Samantha早上到中心交文件和做生物認證，大約需時1小時，形容整個過程戰戰競競。被問到為何首日便到中心辦理手續，Jason說等候申請很久，擔心政府未來或會阻礙市民申請簽證。 Samantha說，數年前已有移民的打算，由於近年的社會事件，決定提早移民。<br />\n<br />\n同樣來辦理手續的張女士形容，近來政治環境不太健康，自己有12歲和10歲的子女，希望較早起行到英國，盡快安排教育和適應新生活。<br />\n<br />\n對於行政會議成員葉劉淑儀表示，中國仍有許多反制選項，例如嚴格執行《國籍法》，針對以BNO入籍英國的人士。張女士表示，最大的關注是展開新生活，小朋友盡快適應，日後沒有投票權都沒辦法，不是她所能控制。"},{"pid":"72f314f25c44e633580711c9ec7a674b1d42f537","tid":2389562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d5060d178f50c5c3056d02dbe706918d918f31","tid":2389562,"uid":64576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"2月23號起用APP就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692deeb3bc002aced62a76f858584e84801b7424","tid":2389562,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:20:13.00